verbose_text: As such, the goal of this study is to understand the variation of TropNO 2 VCDs in East China during the 2005-2020 LNY holiday seasons and quantify contributions by both COVID-19 control measures and clean air regulations to the reduction of TropNO 2 VCDs during 2020 LNY holiday season in East China.
